  Locus:
    Page: 409
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Search/Look Within
---
The path to the source of your and the world’s being is not without. You
have to go within yourself. ‘Seek within and know thyself’; these secret
and sublime hints come to us wafted from the breath of Rishis (wise men)
through the dust of ages.
